    {
      "text": "// The sandbox owns a single global network-ask callback, but UI prompts live\n  // in per-command handlers. Each in-flight sandboxed command pushes itself as\n  // the active target; routeNetworkAsk forwards to the top of the stack. An\n  // empty stack fails closed (deny).\n  pushNetworkAskTarget(target: NetworkAskTarget): void",
      "contextualizedText": "// node/sandbox-manager.ts \u003e interface Sandbox \u003e method pushNetworkAskTarget\n\n// The sandbox owns a single global network-ask callback, but UI prompts live\n  // in per-command handlers. Each in-flight sandboxed command pushes itself as\n  // the active target; routeNetworkAsk forwards to the top of the stack. An\n  // empty stack fails closed (deny).\n  pushNetworkAskTarget(target: NetworkAskTarget): void",
      "headingContext": "node/sandbox-manager.ts \u003e interface Sandbox \u003e method pushNetworkAskTarget",
      "startLine": 40,
      "startCol": 3,
      "endLine": 44,
      "endCol": 55
    },
    {
      "text": "  popNetworkAskTarget(target: NetworkAskTarget): void",
